@NODE Distribution "Distribution"
    I repeat again : this reduced archive is ONLY for Amiga E v3.0
distribution and can't be separated from this last one in any way !
    It must contain the following file structure:

    Bin/Mac2E
    Bin/PreMac2E

    Tools/Mac2E/Mac2E.guide
    Tools/Mac2E/Sources/Mac2E.e
    Tools/Mac2E/Sources/PreMac2E.e
    Tools/Mac2E/ReadMe.first

